HEADWORD: Bombilation
<hw>Bom`bi*la"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A humming
sound; a booming.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To . . . silence the <qex>bombilation</qex> of guns.</q>
